snippet.title: Gods of the Twilight Trailer 2022
snippet.description:
You're a reincarnated god, but that doesn't stop you from being a dork. You don't remember who you truly are, but you'd better figure that out quick, because Ragnarök is coming, and supernatural and government forces have their own ideas about what to do with you. Now see if you can juggle that with your social and romantic life in this episodic visual novel!

Check out the demo!
Steam: https://bit.ly/3mthTqQ
Itch: https://bit.ly/3tIZiKz

More on the game: 
https://twitter.com/godsoftwilight
https://gods-of-the-twilight.tumblr.com
